{"tid":296320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Celine父譚順生個人官網、fb突關閉　忽然不是「Dr.」？","createTime":"2017-06-24T13:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T23:30:34.000Z","uid":5195,"like":94,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ae9e267674237e1f1df2ddd9f3c0965e98ca665","tid":296320,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:03:55.000Z","msg":"近期備受關注的Celine妹妹譚芷昀因為參加《全美一叮》而爆紅，其父譚順生亦成傳媒焦點，最近被踢爆履歷疑似造假、比賽紀錄年份全錯等。香港01記者今日傍晚（24日）發現譚的官方網頁及兩個facebook戶口突然關閉，暫時未知原因。<br />\n<br />\n「小巨肺」Celine譚芷昀父親譚順生連日來被揭醜聞，包括其官方網站所列的獎項紀錄有問題，得獎年份與歌曲推出年份不相符；亦曾在「Tutor kara 」facebook頁面中指，自己畢業於菲律賓馬尼拉大學 （Republic of the Philippines University of Science and Technology），取得商業管理哲學博士學位，惟被網民質疑未能翻查此大學的資料，質疑資料造假。<br />\n<br />\n接連負面報道下，記者今日傍晚發現譚順生的官方網頁（<a href=\"http://tamsteve.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftamsteve.com&d=qluFrNTx%2BHQeHBzS38AkuG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5c1291bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tamsteve.com</a>）及兩個facebook戶口( Tutor kara及karaoketutor drsteve)突然關閉。另外，有報道指，其音樂學校的官網亦不再以「Dr.Steve」稱呼，改為「Steve Tam」。不過，在Google的搜尋介面，其音樂學校的簡介仍保留「Dr.Steve」稱號。"},{"pid":"4640d4af6973c63963b7c0718f07e72917ba50f0","tid":296320,"uid":24513,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:07:18.000Z","msg":"係咪所有菲律賓大學畢業既都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8028986fa09e4b5d0fb48c26f7d4f73591664c44","tid":296320,"uid":6728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:07:59.000Z","msg":"睇條仆街仆街最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5f16d6c11b1a237c7d261adbbdc00035e91f6f","tid":296320,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://tamsteve.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftamsteve.com&d=qluFrNTx%2BHQeHBzS38AkuG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5c1291bd\" target=\"_blank\">tamsteve.com</a></blockquote><br />\n<br 