:296320,"uid":19310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"好想係佢fb留言<br />\n<br />\n人面對風波心中少不免 震震震震震"},{"pid":"5468b41564c0fc2bd3e99dad74c39c9187470ee6","tid":296320,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:17:54.000Z","msg":"點解啲人咁鍾意作自己菲律賓畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0277d2e6ceb980b13d32abec26f43bf7f0be4d5","tid":296320,"uid":80416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:36:24.000Z","msg":"Mister <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\nDoctor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMister Doctor?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIts strange...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n...Maybe.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a12634c0debf22ecc4fd8cc5c5f158dbbb9b3a","tid":296320,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解啲人咁鍾意作自己菲律賓畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇返國力書院嗰單野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7eaa754bf61617e39de05731f2d9d310dbe46f3","tid":296320,"uid":35499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:47:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1498375732161&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20170625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1498375732161%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20170625&d=qluFrNTx%2BHQeHBzS38AkuG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=ed615c6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1498375732161%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20170625&h=186bc59d\" target=\"_blank\">http://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1498375732161&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20170625</a><br />\n<br />\n譚順生今日出席新碟發布會時，拿取出博士畢業證書：「我的確2008年畢業，是博士學位畢業，學校名是Nueva Ecija University of Science and Technology，我說說有博士學位畢業證書的原因，我2013年開歌唱學校之前，於2003年開設獵頭公司，獵頭公司是專門學業，我發覺我需要專業資格，2006年我有機會認識此課程，我用了2年時間，辛苦學習寫論文，2008年畢業，在我朋友及生活圈子，一路用Dr.Steve這個名，用到現在，所以可以說這個博士學位，是完全事實。<br />\n<br />\n2007年Celine出世，發現她喜歡唱歌，我又教唱歌，當時決定栽培她去唱歌，我又好開心和滿足，和太太商量後，決定開一間歌唱學校，因為想幫多些小朋友。」而譚順生手中的畢業證書，顯示其所讀科目是Doctor of Philosophy in Business Administration（工商管理哲學系博士），完全與音樂無關。<br />\n<br />\n之後他又展示學校宣傳資料，資料的內容和字眼，並無提及有關其音樂專業資格，他說：「我好深信每位學生跟我學唱歌的，是因為欣賞我教Celine方法而來，如果有任何人覺得Dr. Steve的名稱，令他們對我的音樂專業資格產生誤會，我只可以深感抱歉，最後好多謝傳媒及朋友，對我同Celine關注，我往後會熟讀《弟子規》，畀心機學習，不斷令自己進步﹑我覺得每個人都有過去，我有好多不足之處，我會決心地用我所有能力，做一個好父親。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06dceb3a506426c48ef385b76db3c23f38cac211","tid":296320,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T08:39:52.000Z","msg":"用慈父轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80e84b9917bc00a9d1432991a50db82bc7b7e52","tid":296320,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T09:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1498375732161&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20170625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1498375732161%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20170625&d=qluFrNTx%2BHQeHBzS38AkuG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=ed615c6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fphp%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1498375732161%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20170625&h=186bc59d\" target=\"_blank\">http://ol.mingpao.com/php/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1498375732161&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=2017062