:296320,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T09:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/173430_f8d6712657a67e8603730c44160a3a4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F173430_f8d6712657a67e8603730c44160a3a4e.jpg&h=0e178593&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c3824ac415bf112115d81f38e98217ddf584306","tid":296320,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T09:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪所有菲律賓大學畢業既都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔係嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢嗰間就肯定假囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好人好者點會讀菲律賓大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多數都有問題㗎喇</blockquote><br />\n以香港人嚟講都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無學校收，要去賓賓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔係嘅，因為聽聞菲律賓牙科係幾出名，你留意下香港有唔小牙醫都係喺嗰邊讀完返嚟</blockquote><br />\n聽你老母咩<br />\n人唔笑狗都吠啦<br />\n牙醫香港全球第一<br />\n柒少陣縮返入你老母子宮度啦</blockquote><br />\n你係味小朋友？"},{"pid":"2044b20b686a0749a58cfe0d02ea37cf6cad41a5","tid":296320,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:04:27.000Z","msg":"又國力 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4cc169375479321c5078c686445ad53d455c1d","tid":296320,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識幾個有錢仔讀唔到醫<br />\n去菲律賓讀牙醫<br />\n而家發過豬頭<br />\n<br />\n利申四十幾歲中坑</blockquote><br />\n菲律賓牙醫係好有認受性<br />\n不過近廿年畀港大爬頭</blockquote><br />\n以前香港冇牙醫，大把人去菲律賓<br />\n五六十年代香港仲窮過鬼嗰陣，東南亞唔少地方有錢過香港，如馬來西亞，菲律賓，南越，所以去菲律賓讀牙醫不奇怪<br />\n<br />\n連登啲細路歷史背景乜鳩都唔知，仲成日話自己有咩國際視野，又笑鳩台狗韓狗，早抖啦<br />\n<br />\n港大&ldquo;爬唔爬頭&rdquo;根本冇討論價值，因為香港醫療霸權專業壟斷 自己玩晒"}]}